# No env vars are required by /api/capture.
#
# Email is sent via the Cloudflare `send_email` binding (Email Routing).
# The recipient (info@accountic.in) and sender (notify@accountic.in) are
# hardcoded in src/pages/api/capture.ts; the SIGNUP_NOTIFY binding is
# configured in wrangler.jsonc.
#
# This file is kept as a placeholder in case future env vars are added.
